{
  "stem": "11723.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On the other hand, my sister and I-- this I remember-- I was very, very ill.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So was my sister.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had measles, a very high fever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, at that time already, Jews were not able to travel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They weren't-- I shouldn't say weren't able.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They weren't allowed to travel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not only did you have to wear the star, but you couldn't leave your place of residence.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I don't mean the house itself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But you couldn't go from Budapest to another city or vice versa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father came down somehow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very hard to get on a train because everybody was trying to get back home or wherever they were going, and there was big panic.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After all, we were under occupation, even the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so my father and my mother got a note from the doctor that we need to be in Budapest because we were so ill, from the pediatrician.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had to wear the star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we went to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, this is my experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we stayed there for a whole day and a whole night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were burning with fever, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was bedlam there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You-- you couldn't move there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody wanted to get on the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every time we got on a train, and they saw the star on my parents, they threw us off the train, and I mean literally threw us off the train.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And finally, my parents decided that they were going to cover up the star.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were not going to tear it off, but cover it up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one of them would carry me on that side.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my mother would carry my sister on that side, covering the star.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
